              </p>

              <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg mt-6 mb-3">6. Meridian Gable (Powered by Thinkrr AI) &mdash; Our Top Pick for HVAC</h3>
              <div class="bg-muted/50 border border-border rounded-lg p-4 my-4">
