              <ul class="text-sm text-foreground/80 mb-4 leading-relaxed list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                <li><strong>AI voice agent answering 24/7</strong> with 80+ natural voice profiles</li>
                <li><strong>Emergency triage and live transfer</strong> with HVAC-specific qualifying questions</li>
