                <a href="https://meridiangable.com" data-affiliate data-vendor="meridiangable" data-position="cta" style="display: inline-block; background: transparent; color: #1B4F72; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; border: 1px solid #1B4F72; margin-left: 8px;">Learn More</a>
