                <strong>Limitations:</strong> No built-in CRM. No outbound calling agents. No website chat on AI plan. No workflow automation. Limited to call answering only.<br/>
                <strong>Pricing:</strong> AI Receptionist starts at $95/mo (50 calls). Overage at $2.40/call. Annual plans include custom voice persona.<br/>
